99875416dd630a4b06a3/img-1662243-1695848838-7999200.png) #### 📝 Tips 用于 finding the 右侧 Facebook Page - If the page name contains spaces, it 可以 帮助 到 replace the space 与 an underscore symbol 何时 您 输入 the name. 用于 example, "运行ner's World" 可能 be 输入d as "运行ners_World" 到 查找 the 右侧 page. - Some brands have multiple Facebook Pages under the same name, making it difficult 到 identify the page 您're looking 用于. [这里's an example](https://分享.aitoearn.com/9ZuE7Le5). Each Facebook Page has an ID, 哪个 is the string of numbers 那个 应用ear 在 the list of matching results. 您 可以 查找 哪个 ID relates 到 哪个 page by heading 到 [https://Facebook.com/](https://Facebook.com/)***page-id-这里*** (哪里 您'd replace ***page-id-这里*** 与 one of 那些 IDs). 您'd then be taken 到 那个 特定的 page. ## X/Twitter mentions Due 到 API limitations, 我们’re not able 到 auto完整的 mentions of X/Twitter 账户s. 那个 said, 您 可以 still include mentions 在 您的 帖子 but 您 将会 need 到 输入 在 the exact handle 您’d like 到 include. Once 您的 帖子 is 发布ed 到 X/Twitter, the 账户 您 mentioned 将会 become hyper链接ed. ## Instagram mentions Due 到 API limitations, 我们’re not able 到 auto完整的 mentions of Instagram 账户s. 那个 said, 您 可以 still include mentions 在 您的 帖子 but 您 将会 need 到 输入 在 the exact handle 您’d like 到 include. 您 可以 include up 到 20 mentions within one 帖子. Once 发布ed 到 Instagram, the 账户 您 mentioned 将会 become hyper链接ed. Interested 在 [tagging people 在 您的 图片s](https://支持.aitoearn.com//支持.aitoearn.com/article/657-scheduling-Instagram-帖子-和-reels#01H7G21HKE58NN5XZSC0Y9JSAG)? Currently, tagging 在 图片s is only 可用 用于 Instagram 帖子 那个 are 发布ed automatically. [学习 更多 about how 图片 tagging works 这里](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/554-using-Instagram-与-aitoearn#01H85TJYNSEZGDDX8DHJP4BAVJ). ❓ 可以 我们的 Customer Advocacy 团队 ans我们r any questions 用于 您? Feel 免费 到 触达 out [这里](mailto:hello@aitoearn.com). ## 链接edIn mentions ### Mentioning 链接edIn Pages 到 mention a 链接edIn Page, 复制 和 粘贴 the 链接edIn 网址 用于 那个 Page into the composer (eg: 到 mention Aitoearn, 您 将会 复制 和 粘贴 我们的 链接edIn 网址 那个 looks like 这个: [https://www.链接edIn.com/company/aitoearn应用/](https://www.链接edIn.com/company/aitoearn应用/).). ![Tagging the Aitoearn 链接edIn company page 在 the Aitoearn composer](//d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/docs/assets/64cb6cf86d4a3e191f237e66/图片s/67dc81e902203579182abc4b/文件-UsoKDxmCcL.gif) ### Mentioning 链接edIn 个人资料s 到 mention a 链接edIn 个人资料, 您 可以 输入 the @ symbol 和 搜索 用于 a 个人资料* 到 tag. ![Tagging a 链接edIn 个人资料 在 the Aitoearn composer](//d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/docs/assets/64cb6cf86d4a3e191f237e66/图片s/682631b8b8fe062cb5e0446e/文件-96x4nxfDP0.png) ***Notes: ** - 链接edIn Pages 可以 only tag 个人资料s 那个 follow their Page. - 链接edIn 个人资料s 可以 only tag 个人资料s belonging 到 their 连接ions. - Because different channels 可能 have different 连接ions, it is not possible 到 选择 multiple 链接edIn channels 何时 @ mentioning a 链接edIn 个人资料. - It is not possible 到 tag 您的 own 链接edIn 个人资料 在 Aitoearn. ### 故障排除 链接edIn 个人资料 mentions If 您're trying 到 tag a 链接edIn 个人资料 but it's not working as expected, 那里 可能 be a few reasons behind 这个. 这里 are some 常见的 scenarios 到 check: #### 1. The 个人资料 isn’t 关注中 您的 链接edIn 组织 page 用于 a tag 到 work, the person 您're trying 到 mention must be 关注中 您的 company’s 链接edIn page. **如何 verify:** - As the Page 管理员, go 到 您的 company page, 点击 在 the number of 关注者, 和 搜索 用于 the name of the person 您're trying 到 mention. - Alternatively, the person 您're trying 到 mention 可以 verify if they're 关注中 您的 page. #### 2. The 个人资料 has 个人资料 visibility turned off If someone has restricted their 个人资料 visibility, they 可能 not 应用ear as an option 到 mention 何时 您're composing a 帖子. #### 3. Third-party data sharing is turned off 链接edIn allows 用户s 到 limit how their data is 分享d 与 external tools 和 services. If 这个 setting is 已禁用, it 可以 prevent them from being mentioned out侧边 of 链接edIn directly. #### 4. Mentions are 已禁用 在 their 账户 链接edIn 用户s 可以 选择 到 prevent others from mentioning them 在 帖子 或 评论. If 这个 setting is off, they won’t be taggable. #### 5. The 个人资料 has restricted access 到 their 个人资料 If the person 您’re trying 到 tag has blocked 您 或 set their 个人资料 visibility so 您 可以’t view it, 您 won’t be able 到 tag them. **Note: **Items 2-5 在 the above list 可以 only be verified by the 链接edIn 个人资料 owner within their 账户 设置. 那里fore, if 您've confirmed 那个 the 个人资料 is 关注中 您的 Page, 您 可以 ask the 个人资料 owner 到 check the 关注中: - If 那里 is any missing piece of information about the 个人资料 being tagged, including First Name, Last Name, 或 Headline. - If 您 are trying 到 match a 个人资料 您 want 到 tag based 在 the Maiden Name 或 添加itional Name, 那个 information is not publicly visible. - 在 case 那里 are any misspelled characters, hidden spaces 在 the name, etc. - If the 用户’s 个人资料 您 are tagging is not 在 EN_US, it won’t be returned under suggestions. ## Mastodon mentions 您 可以 mention 用户s by typing out their full 添加ress, e.g. @jane@示例erver.com. Note 那个 any usage of @word 将会 be interpreted as mentioning the local 用户 与 the 用户name word, if 那个 用户 exists. Only the 用户name part 将会 count against 您的 character limit - the domain is not counted. ## TikTok mentions 您 可以 mention a TikTok 用户 by typing out their exact handle 在 the caption of 您的 帖子 (e.g. @‌aitoearn应用). Once 发布ed 到 TikTok, the 账户 您 mentioned 将会 become hyper链接ed. ## Threads mentions 在 这个 time, 我们’re not able 到 auto完整的 mentions of Threads 或 Instagram 账户s. 那个 said, 您 可以 still include mentions 在 您的 Threads 帖子 but 您 将会 need 到 输入 在 the exact handle 您’d like 到 include. Once 发布ed, the mention 应该 be hyper链接ed. ## Bluesky mentions Tag other 用户s by inputting their full handle, eg: @name.bsky.social. 我们 don’t currently offer auto完整的 of handles, so make sure 到 输入 the handle correctly, 或 复制/粘贴 from their page!
